        {
            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/10/mysql%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/10/mysql%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0/",
            "title": "mysql语句总结",
            "date_published": "2023-11-09T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"课堂复习题\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#课堂复习题\">#</a> 课堂复习题</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>已知三张表如下:<br>\n 学生 (学号、姓名、班级、年龄)<br>\n 课程 (课号、课名、学分)<br>\n 选课 (学号、课号、成绩)<br>\n 请完成以下练习题:<br>\n1、把数据库原理及应用课程成绩增加 10 分。<br>\n2、删除李四同学的选课记录。<br>\n3、 显示数据库原理及应用的学生成绩<br>\n 4、查询每个学生选修课程的学号、课程名称和成绩。<br>\n5、查询每个同学的学号，姓名，总学分。(成绩及格的才能拿到学分)<br>\n 6、找出每个学生超过他所有的选修课程的平均成绩的课程号。<br>\n7、查询每个班、每门课程的平均分</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>1. 把数据库原理及应用课程成绩增加 10 分。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">UPDATE</span> 选课  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SET</span> 成绩 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 成绩 <span class=\"operator\">+</span> <span class=\"number\">10</span>  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 课号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 课号 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 课程 <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 课名 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;数据库原理及应用&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2. 删除李四同学的选课记录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">DELETE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 选课  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 学号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 学号 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 学生 <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 姓名 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;李四&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3. 显示数据库原理及应用的学生成绩</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 学生.学号, 学生.姓名, 选课.成绩   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 学生   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 选课 <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 学生.学号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 选课.学号   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 课程 <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 选课.课号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 课程.课号   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 课程.课名 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;数据库原理及应用&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>4. 查询每个学生选修课程的学号、课程名称和成绩。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">select</span> 学生.学号, 课程.课名, 选课.成绩</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 学生   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 选课 <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 学生.学号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 选课.学号   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 课程 <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 选课.课号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 课程.课号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"多表查询\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#多表查询\">#</a> 多表查询</h1>\n<p>1. 查询每个同学的总学分，成绩大于等于 60 才能拿到学分，以中文显示学号、姓名、总学分，以学号升序排列。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">select</span> s.sno <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> 学号, s.sn <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> 姓名, coalesec(<span class=\"built_in\">sum</span>(credit)) <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> 总学分</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> s</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"keyword\">join</span> sc <span class=\"keyword\">on</span> s.sno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> sc.sno</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"keyword\">join</span> c <span class=\"keyword\">on</span> sc.cno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> c.cno <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> sc.score<span class=\"operator\">&gt;=</span><span class=\"number\">60</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">group</span> <span class=\"keyword\">by</span> 学号,姓名</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"keyword\">by</span> 总学分;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>",
            "tags": [
                "mysql"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/06/python/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/06/python/",
            "title": "Python做题笔记",
            "date_published": "2023-11-05T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"函数\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#函数\">#</a> 函数</h1>\n<h2 id=\"输入\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#输入\">#</a> 输入</h2>\n<h3 id=\"input\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#input\">#</a> input()</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">a = <span class=\"built_in\">input</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;input:&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>可以输入</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">input</span>:<span class=\"number\">123</span>  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">input</span>:runoob  <span class=\"comment\">#a都是字符串</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>输入一个数字</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">a = <span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">input</span>())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"处理输入的一长串数字\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#处理输入的一长串数字\">#</a> 处理输入的一长串数字</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p red'>map()</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">map</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>, <span class=\"built_in\">input</span>().split())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p red'>list()</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">map</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>, <span class=\"built_in\">input</span>().split()))  <span class=\"comment\"># 输入n个分数并存入列表 </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p red'>sort()</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>对列表进行升序排序</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">list</span>.sort()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>去掉最高分和最低分 (左闭右开)</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight py\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">list</span> = <span class=\"built_in\">list</span>[<span class=\"number\">1</span>:-<span class=\"number\">1</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"打印\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#打印\">#</a> 打印</h2>\n<h3 id=\"保留小数\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#保留小数\">#</a> 保留小数</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p red'>round()</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">round</span>(计算表达式,保留位数)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">round</span>(a/b,<span class=\"number\">2</span>) <span class=\"comment\">#保留2位小数</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>或者在打印时保留</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;aver=&#123;:.2f&#125;&#x27;</span>.<span class=\"built_in\">format</span>(aver))</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(<span class=\"string\">f&#x27;aver=<span class=\"subst\">&#123;aver:<span class=\"number\">.2</span>f&#125;</span>&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"对列表数据进行处理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#对列表数据进行处理\">#</a> 对列表数据进行处理</h2>\n<h3 id=\"计算\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#计算\">#</a> 计算</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sum</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>) <span class=\"comment\">#计算总和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>) <span class=\"comment\">#计算长度</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>list () 可以把列表中的整形元素取出来当做数字处理</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"-swig24-\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-swig24-\">#</a> <span class='p red'>判断列表中是否有重复元素</span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p cyan'>能够删除列表中的重复元素</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">x = <span class=\"built_in\">set</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;runoob&#x27;</span>) <span class=\"comment\">#删除重复元素</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt;&gt;&gt;x = <span class=\"built_in\">set</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;runoob&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>y = <span class=\"built_in\">set</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;google&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x, y</span><br><span class=\"line\">(<span class=\"built_in\">set</span>([<span class=\"string\">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;n&#x27;</span>]), <span class=\"built_in\">set</span>([<span class=\"string\">&#x27;e&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;g&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;l&#x27;</span>]))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p cyan'>判断列表中是否有重复元素</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>使用了判断列表长度的方法，真是想不到，我第一想法是两个循环</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title function_\">check</span>(<span class=\"params\"><span class=\"built_in\">list</span></span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>) != <span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">set</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 包含重复元素则不相等，返回true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"大写\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#大写\">#</a> 大写</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">a.upper()</span><br><span class=\"line\">a.isupper() <span class=\"comment\"># 判断是否大写</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"把一个整数每一位分开变成列表\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#把一个整数每一位分开变成列表\">#</a> 把一个整数每一位分开变成列表</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p red'>str()</span>    返回一个对象的string格式。\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title function_\">integer_to_list</span>(<span class=\"params\">n</span>):  </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">str</span>(n))  <span class=\"comment\"># 列表里的元素是字符串</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># return [int(i) for i in str(n)]  </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># 把数字转换成字符串，再把每个字符转换成整数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">n = <span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">input</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;请输入一个4位整数：&quot;</span>))  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(integer_to_list(n))   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"可变参数\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#可变参数\">#</a> 可变参数</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>参数前带一个 * 号（元祖）</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title function_\">sum_func</span>(<span class=\"params\">*args</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">sum</span>(args)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">result = sum_func(<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">2</span>, <span class=\"number\">3</span>, <span class=\"number\">7</span>, <span class=\"number\">4</span>, <span class=\"number\">5</span>, <span class=\"number\">6</span>)  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(result)  <span class=\"comment\"># 输出：28</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<span class='p cyan'>args为可变参数，其可接受若干个实参值，并将接收到的值组装为一个元组。</span>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>有时候用内置函数 sum () 会报错，只能手动循环</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title function_\">sum_func</span>(<span class=\"params\">*args</span>):  </span><br><span class=\"line\">    total = <span class=\"number\">0</span>  </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> num <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> args:  </span><br><span class=\"line\">        total += num  </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> total  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">result = sum_func(<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">2</span>, <span class=\"number\">3</span>, <span class=\"number\">7</span>, <span class=\"number\">4</span>, <span class=\"number\">5</span>, <span class=\"number\">6</span>)  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(result)  <span class=\"comment\"># 输出：28</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p cyan'>两个*号代表字典</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"易错\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#易错\">#</a> 易错</h1>\n<h2 id=\"逻辑与逻辑或\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#逻辑与逻辑或\">#</a> 逻辑与，逻辑或</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class='p blue'>只能用and和or</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"整除\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#整除\">#</a> 整除</h2>\n<span class='p red'>负整数整除结果与正整数整除结果不同</span>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">a = -<span class=\"number\">11</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">b = <span class=\"number\">11</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(a//<span class=\"number\">10</span>)  <span class=\"comment\"># -2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(b//<span class=\"number\">10</span>) <span class=\"comment\"># 1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>对于 a，因为 - 11 除以 10 等于 - 1.1，然后向下取整结果为 - 2</strong></p>\n<span class='p blue'>要想结果保持一致可以用绝对值</span>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">a = <span class=\"built_in\">abs</span>(a)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(a//<span class=\"number\">10</span>) <span class=\"comment\"># 1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"斐波那契数列\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#斐波那契数列\">#</a> 斐波那契数列</h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title function_\">fibo</span>(<span class=\"params\">n</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">list</span> = [<span class=\"number\">1</span>]  <span class=\"comment\"># 这里创建列表时必须添加一个1，不然结果不对</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    a, b = <span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"built_in\">range</span>(n-<span class=\"number\">1</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">        a, b = b, a+b</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">list</span>.append(a)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">list</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">n = <span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">input</span>())</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(fibo(n))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>",
            "tags": []
        },
        {
            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/04/JS/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/04/JS/",
            "title": "js百炼成仙总结",
            "date_published": "2023-11-03T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"基础\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#基础\">#</a> 基础</h1>\n<h2 id=\"对象数据类型\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#对象数据类型\">#</a> 对象数据类型</h2>\n<h3 id=\"创建\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#创建\">#</a> 创建</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> container = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcaoyao : <span class=\"string\">&quot;解毒草&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">feijain</span>: <span class=\"string\">&quot;乌木剑&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var container = &#123;&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">container.caoyao = &quot;解毒草&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">container.feijian = &quot;乌木剑&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"调用对象中的属性\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#调用对象中的属性\">#</a> 调用对象中的属性</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>当调用的是一个中括号就需要用 []</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var container = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcaoyao : &quot;解毒草&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfeijain: &quot;乌木剑&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">var prop = &quot;caoyao&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">console.log(container[prop])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"遍历对象\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#遍历对象\">#</a> 遍历对象</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>typeof()<br>\n 定义一个对象时后面要加分好，定义函数不用</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var a = &quot;123&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">var fun = function()&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">console.log(typeof(a));</span><br><span class=\"line\">console.log(typeof(fun));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202311071940503.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2023-11-07 193954\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>遍历对象获得属性名称</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> yexiaofan = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    name : <span class=\"string\">&quot;叶小凡&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    age : <span class=\"number\">16</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    eat : <span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;KFCvm50&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> yexiaofan)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(p)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">name</span><br><span class=\"line\">age</span><br><span class=\"line\">eat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>遍历对象获得值</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> yexiaofan)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(p + <span class=\"string\">&quot;=&quot;</span> + yexiaofan[p]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"数组\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#数组\">#</a> 数组</h2>\n<h3 id=\"数组的定义\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#数组的定义\">#</a> 数组的定义</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>直接定义</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var arr = [&quot;first&quot;,&quot;second&quot;,&quot;third&quot;];</span><br><span class=\"line\">console.log(arr)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>构造函数创建数组</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var arr = new Array(8);</span><br><span class=\"line\">console.log(a.length)  //8,数组只有一个length属性</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"数组内置函数\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#数组内置函数\">#</a> 数组内置函数</h3>\n",
            "tags": []
        },
        {
            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/03/nodejs/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/03/nodejs/",
            "title": "nodejs学习",
            "date_published": "2023-11-02T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"nodejs\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#nodejs\">#</a> nodejs</h1>\n<h2 id=\"eval\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#eval\">#</a> eval()</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>在 nodejs 中，eval () 方法用于计算字符串，并把它作为脚本代码来执行</li>\n<li>执行系统命令的方法</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">execSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;ls&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">execSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;cat f*&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">execSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;ls&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">toString</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">execSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;cat fl00g.txt&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">toString</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">spawnSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;ls&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"property\">stdout</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">toString</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">spawnSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;ls&#x27;</span>,[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>]).<span class=\"property\">stdout</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">toString</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">spawnSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;ls&#x27;</span>,[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;./&#x27;</span>]).<span class=\"property\">stdout</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">toString</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">spawnSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;cat&#x27;</span>,[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;fl00g.txt&#x27;</span>]).<span class=\"property\">stdout</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">toString</span>()  <span class=\"comment\">//不能通配符</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">spawnSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;cat&#x27;</span>,[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;fl00g.txt&#x27;</span>]).<span class=\"property\">stdout</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">toString</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">?<span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>=<span class=\"variable language_\">global</span>.<span class=\"property\">process</span>.<span class=\"property\">mainModule</span>.<span class=\"property\">constructor</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">_load</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;child_process&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">execSync</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;ls&#x27;</span>,[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>]).<span class=\"title function_\">toString</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"prototype-原型链污染攻击\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#prototype-原型链污染攻击\">#</a> Prototype 原型链污染攻击</h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1.prototype是一个类的属性，所有类对象在实例化的时候将会拥有prototype中的属性和方法</span><br><span class=\"line\">2.一个对象的__proto__属性，指向这个对象所在的类的prototype属性</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>所有类对象在实例化的时候将会拥有 prototype 中的属性和方法，这个特性被用来实现 JavaScript 中的继承机制。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"javascript原型链继承\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#javascript原型链继承\">#</a> JavaScript 原型链继承</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">Father</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"property\">first_name</span> = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;Donald&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"property\">last_name</span> = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;Trump&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">Son</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"property\">first_name</span> = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;Melania&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title class_\">Son</span>.<span class=\"property\"><span class=\"keyword\">prototype</span></span> = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Father</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> son = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Son</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"string\">`Name: <span class=\"subst\">$&#123;son.first_name&#125;</span> <span class=\"subst\">$&#123;son.last_name&#125;</span>`</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<p>对于对象 son，在调用 son.last_name 的时候，实际上 JavaScript 引擎会进行如下操作：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1.在对象son中寻找last_name</span><br><span class=\"line\">2.如果找不到，则在son.__proto__中寻找last_name</span><br><span class=\"line\">3.如果仍然找不到，则继续在son.__proto__.__proto__中寻找last_name</span><br><span class=\"line\">4.依次寻找，直到找到null结束。比如，Object.prototype的__proto__就是null</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>prototype 继承链</strong>：</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">每个构造函数(constructor)都有一个原型对象(prototype)</span><br><span class=\"line\">对象的__proto__属性，指向类的原型对象prototype</span><br><span class=\"line\">JavaScript使用prototype链实现继承机制</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"原型污染链\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#原型污染链\">#</a> 原型污染链</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">既然foo.<span class=\"property\">__proto__</span>指向的是<span class=\"title class_\">Foo</span>类的prototype，通过修改foo.<span class=\"property\">__proto__</span>就可以修改原型<span class=\"title class_\">Object</span>类</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// foo是一个简单的JavaScript对象</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> foo = &#123;<span class=\"attr\">bar</span>: <span class=\"number\">1</span>&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// foo.bar 此时为1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(foo.<span class=\"property\">bar</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 修改foo的原型（即Object）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">foo.<span class=\"property\">__proto__</span>.<span class=\"property\">bar</span> = <span class=\"number\">2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 由于查找顺序的原因，foo.bar仍然是1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(foo.<span class=\"property\">bar</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 此时再用Object创建一个空的zoo对象</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> zoo = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 查看zoo.bar</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(zoo.<span class=\"property\">bar</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>我的理解是如果攻击者控制并修改了一个对象的原型（如上述的 Object 类），就可以影响这个原型下的所有子类</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"哪些情况下会被污染\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#哪些情况下会被污染\">#</a> 哪些情况下会被污染？</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>可以设置 <code>__proto__</code> 的值的情况：<br>\n<strong> <code>找找能够控制数组（对象）的“键名”的操作</code> </strong></li>\n</ul>\n <figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">merge</span>(<span class=\"params\">target, source</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">let</span> key <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> source) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (key <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> source &amp;&amp; key <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> target) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"title function_\">merge</span>(target[key], source[key])</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            target[key] = source[key]</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>要让 <code>__proto__</code> 被认为是一个键</p>\n <figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> o1 = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> o2 = <span class=\"title class_\">JSON</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">parse</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#123;&quot;a&quot;: 1, &quot;__proto__&quot;: &#123;&quot;b&quot;: 2&#125;&#125;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">merge</span>(o1, o2)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(o1.<span class=\"property\">a</span>, o1.<span class=\"property\">b</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">o3 = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(o3.<span class=\"property\">b</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/StarofEden/blog@main/image1/20220710123750_11cf1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "JavaScript",
